            <a href="http://kam.mff.cuni.cz/">Department of Applied Mathematics</a> (hardware),
            <a href="http://www.msmt.cz/index.php?lang=2">Ministry of Education, Youth and Sports</a>&nbsp;(co-announcer),
            <a href="http://interlos.fi.muni.cz/">Interlos</a> (the game engine) and
            <a href="http://www.cez.cz/en/home.html">CEZ Group</a> (sponsorship).
        </p>
    </div>
</div>

